# graphify-specific ignores (gitignore syntax)
# See https://github.com/safishamsi/graphify for the tool itself.

# Go vendored dependencies — third-party code, not ours.
# Workaround for upstream gap: graphify's hardcoded _SKIP_DIRS doesn't include vendor/.
# Without this rule, ~1700 files of vendored deps dominate the graph.
vendor/

# Operator credentials file. Graphify's secret-detection regex
# (\b(credential|secret|...)s?\b) misses this filename because `_` is a
# word character in regex, so there's no word boundary inside
# `chain_credentials`. File is chmod 600 + gitignored, but belt-and-braces.
.chain_credentials.txt
